Interface JointR1CombinationEngine

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JointR1NormalCombinationEngine
    public interface JointR1CombinationEngine
    JointR1CombinationEngine implements the Engine that generates the Combined/Posterior Distributions from the Prior and the Conditional Joint Multivariate R1 Distributions.

    • Module = Numerical Core Module
    • Library = Numerical Optimizer Library
